Heat the oven to 200C/400F/Gas 6.Put the aubergine on a baking sheet and roast in the oven for 30-40 minutes until tender. Cool and pull off the skin.Put the aubergine flesh in a food processor with the garlic, lemon juice, zest and coriander. Season well and whiz together.With the motor still running, pour in the olive oil and blend until the mixture is smooth.